headline.print_headline: Europeans Petkovic and Cepelova Make Charleston Final
headline.main: Europeans Petkovic and Cepelova Make Charleston Final

lead_paragraph: Bosnian-born German Andrea Petkovic outlasted rising Canadian star Eugenie Bouchard in a Family Circle Cup semi-final on Saturday to earn a spot in a WTA final for the eighth time.
